Type: Package
Package: uci
Title: Urban Centrality Index
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Rafael H. M.", "Pereira", , "rafa.pereira.br@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2125-7465"))
           )
Description: Calculates the Urban Centrality Index (UCI) as in Pereira et al., 
             (2013) <https://doi.org/10.1111/gean.12002>. The UCI measures the 
             extent to which the spatial organization of a city or region varies 
             from extreme monocentric to extreme polycentric in a continuous 
             scale from 0 to 1. Values close to 0 indicate more polycentric patterns
             and values close to 1 indicate a more monocentric urban form.
